article_title: Lunchbox: Feel Food Offers Healthy, Tasty Dishes
article_text:
Healthy food makes you feel good, but can it taste good, too?

With a new cafe in Union Square called Feel Food, restaurateurs Fernando Aciar and Gaeleen Quinn are setting out to prove that it isn't necessary to sacrifice big, indulgent flavors to eat right.

The concept may not sound revolutionary, but for people battling food allergies...
